p:
Baseline assessments to be carried out on day 0, immediately prior to harvest include:



Clinical assessment;



Baseline questionnaire on demographics and comorbidity/concomitant medication;



Victorian Institute of Sports Assessment Achilles (VISA-A) Questionnaire;



Visual Analogue Score (VAS);



Manchester Oxford Foot and Ankle Questionnaire (MOXFQ);



EuroQol 5-dimension 5-level (EQ-5D-5L) Questionnaire;



Sporting Activity Score (SAS);



Ultrasound imaging and UTC;



Adverts events (AE) review.
